  to see all rake tasks having the name 'db' in it
  example: rake db:create
           rake db:migrate

rake -D db

  to print out detail description for the tasks having the name 'db' in it


rake --help

  to show the rake help message</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
